text:
This is the kind that is really hidden gem!
was skeptical at the signboard no msg, but for sure after meal even reach home i dont feel thirsty. black chicken soup is flavourful and sweet from the red dates added. pricing in general are value for money. went back for more than 3 times before deciding its worth the 5 star.
This herbal chicken soup is very tasty with traditional herbs. The chicken is very fresh, likely is kampong chicken. Really additive. Must try.
